ЁЯФН Question: тАЬWhat is the parent folder for modules/?тАЭ

ЁЯСЙ The parent folder of the modules/ directory is the terraform/ folder itself.

In other words:

Folder	Role
terraform/	Parent (contains root module + modules folder)
terraform/modules/	Child folder
terraform/modules/vpc	Grandchild folder (actual child module code)
==================
Q. what is root , child & published module ?
