тЪЩя╕П Types of Connectivity in NAT Gateway? 
Type	Meaning	Use Case
ЁЯМН Public NAT Gateway	Connected to Internet Gateway (IGW) тАФ uses Elastic IP	When Private Subnets need to access the internet
ЁЯФТ Private NAT Gateway	Connected via Private Link (no Internet Gateway) тАФ no Elastic IP	When Private Subnets in different VPCs or on-prem** need to communicate securely (no internet)**
===============================================
ЁЯзйQ. Does NAT Gateway create an ENI (Elastic Network Interface)?
тЬЕ Yes.
When you create a NAT Gateway in AWS:

AWS automatically creates an Elastic Network Interface (ENI) for the NAT Gateway.

This ENI is placed in the subnet where you are creating the NAT Gateway.

It gets assigned a private IP from the subnetтАЩs CIDR.

If itтАЩs a Public NAT Gateway, the ENI is associated with the Elastic IP you allocated.
==========================================
